Wally (Milo Manheim), Charley (Nick Pugliese), Rhonda (Sarah Yarkin), Yuri (Miles Elliot), and Quinn (Ci Hang Ma) must race through their scars to save Janet (Jess Gabor) from Mr. Martin (Josh Zuckerman). Rhonda, Charley, and Wally revisit the places of their deaths - the guidance counselor's office, the school cafeteria, and the football field.
